data.Name: Jon Keleher
data.staff_bio: Jon Keleher is an Administrative Assistant and the receptionist for ICI. With support from the Concord Area Special Education Collaborative (CASE), he was one of the first to participate in regular classes in Concord Public Schools. He graduated from the Transition Program, a Life Skills program, at Middlesex Community College in 2006. He now lives in a One-Bedroom house by himself. Jon himself has a disability and has conquered many obstacles, much to the surprise and joy of those close to him, not to mention himself.
